long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Cars Movement is a pretty and easy action game where your goal is to compare the colors of the cars with the blocks. This action game starts off slow and easy but then accelerates as you begin matching cars. Play again and defeat your recent score or best score. Collect as many rubies as you can to open cool character skins for your ball.

To play this action game, look to the underside of the monitor to see the 4 colors. A vertical line of cars will start driving down with the similar colors as your digital keyboard. Using your mouse, click on the same color as the one coming to you. 

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Cars Movement Browser  Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
